data.description: Welcome to your own paradise! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home offers the perfect blend of luxury and convenience. You'll love the stunning private study with its own patio; it's perfect for working from home or just getting away from it all. The primary suite is a true oasis with a large walk-in shower and whirlpool tub so you can relax in style after a long day. Not to mention, the plush upgraded carpet in the private suite adds to the overall opulence. The spacious bonus room upstairs is complete with a full bath. This space is a perfect hang out when hosting, or for when you just need to escape and relax. When you feel like venturing out, you can take advantage of the community pool! Plus, this half acre wooded lot with 17 trees, provides plenty of space for outdoor activities or peaceful evenings spent stargazing on your own private escape. With 3208 sqft of living space, there's something here for everyone! Make this dreamy property yours today!
